# Anthropic: a REAL secret. Leave this blank in any committed file.
# Easiest path for a private demo: leave blank here and paste the key in the
# app's Setup tab (kept in memory for the session only, never persisted).
# If you set it here for local convenience, note that `vite build` would bake it
# into the public bundle, so do not do that for a shared/public deploy.
VITE_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
